==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Finespun
<hw>Fine"spun`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Spun so as to be
fine; drawn to a fine thread; attenuated; hence, unsubstantial;
visionary; <as>as, <ex>finespun</ex> theories</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Finesse</ent>⟦br⟧
